replies.body:
@Meddler, about the {{champion:127}} changes: Why you guys simply can't lower the cost on her Q in the early levels? 85 mana is  waay too much for an ability that has short range, has low cooldown and pretty low damage as well. 

Make it something like : 65/70/75/85/90. This would help her a lot in the laning phase, while she'd still have to manage her reserves carefully later in the game. 

And one more thing, is someone working on her passive changes or that project is scrapped?
